{"div":{"@xmlns":"http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0","@type":"article","@xml:id":"MG-1681-09_211","head":{"value":"Sur la Fievre d’Amarante","id":"/div/head"},"bibl":{"title":{"value":"Mercure galant","id":"/div/bibl/title"},"#":{"value":", septembre 1681 [tome 10], p. 211-218.","id":"/div/bibl/#"}},"p":{"value":"Je laisse les Nouvelles Etrangeres, pour vous en donner une de nos plus belles Provinces. C’est du Languedoc que je veux parler. Une jeune Dame, qui fait un des ornemens de la Capitale, ayant esté attaquée pendant quelques jours d’une Fievre lente, a veu tout le monde s’intéresser dans son mal. Au Portrait qu’on m’en a fait, elle mérite les vœux qu’on a faits par tout pour elle. Ce qui la met au dessus de beaucoup d’aimables Personnes de son Sexe, est une douceur qui enchante, une langueur, &amp; un je-ne-sçay quoy de tendre &amp; d’engageant dans les yeux, dans le visage, &amp; dans tout ce qu’elle fait, qu’on n’a jamais veu qu’en elle seule. Un galant Homme, qui a esté plus affligé luy seul de ce que sa Fievre luy faisoit soufrir, que tous les autres ensemble, n’eut pas plutost sçeu qu’elle estoit diminuée, que d’une extréme douleur, on le vit passer à une joye excessive. Les premiers transports que luy donna cette joye, furent trop forts pour luy laisser déguiser les sentimens de son cœur. Il les fit paroître dans ces Vers, que vous verrez aisément avoir esté inspirez par une Divinité qui sçait éclairer l’esprit. Je voudrois, Madame, vous en pouvoir envoyer souvent d’aussi agreables.","id":"/div/p"},"quote":{"#":[{"label":{"value":"SUR LA FIEVRE D’AMARANTE.","id":"/div/quote/#[0]/label"}},{"lg":{"l":[{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Enfin, tu peux à tes Loix,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[0]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Amour, soûmettre Amarante,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[1]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et vaincre, si tu m’en crois,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[2]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Son humeur indiférente.","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[3]/hi/#"}}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[2]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"En apprenant le secret","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[0]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"De surprendre cette Belle,","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[1]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Souviens-toy du feu discret","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[2]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Dont mon cœur brûle pour elle.","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[3]/hi/#"}}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[4]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"La Fievre depuis huit jours","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[0]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Chez cette aimable Bergere,","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[1]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Au grand mépris des Amours,","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[2]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Fait ce que tu devrois faire.","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[3]/hi/#"}}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[6]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Sans respect du Medecin","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[0]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Qui la sert de tout son zele,","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[1]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Elle allume dans son sein","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[2]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Sans cesse une ardeur nouvelle.","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[3]/hi/#"}}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[8]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Garantis tant de trésors","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[0]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Du Destin qui les menace ;","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[1]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Chasse-la de ce beau Corps,","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[2]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et va te mettre en sa place.","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[3]/hi/#"}}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[10]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Tu peux luy joüer ce tour","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[0]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Plus aisément qu’il ne semble,","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[1]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Puis que la Fievre &amp; l’Amour","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[2]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ont un grand raport ensemble.","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[3]/hi/#"}}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[12]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Va faire autant de fracas","id":"/div/quote/#[13]/lg/l[0]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Que cette Hostesse cruelle ;","id":"/div/quote/#[13]/lg/l[1]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Il n’est personne icy-bas","id":"/div/quote/#[13]/lg/l[2]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Qui ne te prenne pour elle.","id":"/div/quote/#[13]/lg/l[3]/hi/#"}}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[14]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Tes accés sont vehémens ;","id":"/div/quote/#[15]/lg/l[0]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Tu jettes les plus rebelles","id":"/div/quote/#[15]/lg/l[1]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Dans de grands redoublemens,","id":"/div/quote/#[15]/lg/l[2]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Apres des langueurs mortelles.","id":"/div/quote/#[15]/lg/l[3]/hi/#"}}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[16]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Les flâmes &amp; les glaçons","id":"/div/quote/#[17]/lg/l[0]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Sont de tes moindres boutades ;","id":"/div/quote/#[17]/lg/l[1]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Les chaleurs &amp; les frissons","id":"/div/quote/#[17]/lg/l[2]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Accompagnent tes Malades.","id":"/div/quote/#[17]/lg/l[3]/hi/#"}}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[18]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Sans beaucoup dissimuler,","id":"/div/quote/#[19]/lg/l[0]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Tu peux entrer dans son ame ;","id":"/div/quote/#[19]/lg/l[1]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Accoûtumée à brûler,","id":"/div/quote/#[19]/lg/l[2]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Elle soufrira ta flâme.","id":"/div/quote/#[19]/lg/l[3]/hi/#"}}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[20]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Tu vois bien que sur son cœur","id":"/div/quote/#[21]/lg/l[0]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Tes entreprises sont vaines ;","id":"/div/quote/#[21]/lg/l[1]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Tu n’en seras le vainqueur","id":"/div/quote/#[21]/lg/l[2]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Qu’en te glissant dans ses veines.","id":"/div/quote/#[21]/lg/l[3]/hi/#"}}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[22]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Jusqu’icy tous tes appas","id":"/div/quote/#[23]/lg/l[0]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"N’ont rien pû sur sa franchise ;","id":"/div/quote/#[23]/lg/l[1]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Encor, je n’en répons pas,","id":"/div/quote/#[23]/lg/l[2]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Si tu n’uses de surprise.","id":"/div/quote/#[23]/lg/l[3]/hi/#"}}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[24]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Si tu veux donc t’assurer","id":"/div/quote/#[25]/lg/l[0]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"D’une si belle conqueste,","id":"/div/quote/#[25]/lg/l[1]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Prens le temps qu’à soûpirer","id":"/div/quote/#[25]/lg/l[2]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Son mal la rend toûjours preste.","id":"/div/quote/#[25]/lg/l[3]/hi/#"}}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[26]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Sers-toy de ces mesmes traits","id":"/div/quote/#[27]/lg/l[0]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Qui causent mon mal extréme ;","id":"/div/quote/#[27]/lg/l[1]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"On n’en échape jamais,","id":"/div/quote/#[27]/lg/l[2]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Je le connois par moy-mesme.","id":"/div/quote/#[27]/lg/l[3]/hi/#"}}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[28]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"À ton aimable poison","id":"/div/quote/#[29]/lg/l[0]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Fais céder sa Fievre lente ;","id":"/div/quote/#[29]/lg/l[1]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ce sera la guérison","id":"/div/quote/#[29]/lg/l[2]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"De la divine Amarante.","id":"/div/quote/#[29]/lg/l[3]/hi/#"}}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[30]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"On ne voit que trop icy","id":"/div/quote/#[31]/lg/l[0]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Que les Fievres sont mortelles ;","id":"/div/quote/#[31]/lg/l[1]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Tes atteintes, Dieu mercy,","id":"/div/quote/#[31]/lg/l[2]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ne font plus mourir les Belles.","id":"/div/quote/#[31]/lg/l[3]/hi/#"}}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[32]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Tant de feu qu’il te plaira,","id":"/div/quote/#[33]/lg/l[0]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Quelque brûlant qu’il puisse estre,","id":"/div/quote/#[33]/lg/l[1]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Amarante en guérira,","id":"/div/quote/#[33]/lg/l[2]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"J’ay l’honneur de la connoistre.","id":"/div/quote/#[33]/l